# Animation Rules

## Philosophy
Subtle, purposeful, fast. Healthcare context — never bouncy or flashy.

## Durations
- Micro-interaction: 150-200ms
- Content reveal: 300-500ms
- Modal: 200-300ms
- Stagger delay: 50-100ms between children

## Reduced Motion (Required)
```typescript
const prefersReducedMotion = useReducedMotion();
initial={prefersReducedMotion ? false : { opacity: 0, y: 20 }}
```

## Allowed
- Fade-in + subtle upward translate on scroll (`viewport={{ once: true }}`)
- Staggered card grid reveals
- Mobile menu slide-in
- Modal opacity transition

## Prohibited
- Parallax scrolling
- Bounce, wiggle, shake effects
- Auto-playing looping animations
- Character-by-character text animation
- Animating above-fold content (hurts LCP)

## Performance
- Lazy load: `dynamic(() => import('framer-motion'))`
- Animate `opacity` and `transform` only
- Max 10-15 animated elements per viewport
